{"id": 438, "genre": 1001, "title": "你遇到过Uber司机是啥样的？", "description": "有一种微妙……的贴心。", "record_count": 1560, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160702183722q2dYGKfi97XgW4hc.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-07-23T13:46:55Z", "options": [{"id": 4154, "content": "超爱说：加个微信吧！", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4155, "content": "表示自己是土豪，分分钟赚几十万。", "image": null, "praise_count": 59, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4156, "content": "比出租车司机温柔有礼貌太多……", "image": null, "praise_count": 317, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4153, "content": "好像都不太懂路，各种找不到。", "image": null, "praise_count": 279, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4497, "content": "标准uber司机。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145418}, {"id": 4532, "content": "和男朋友在Uber上吵架 结果司机给了我四颗星 活活把我五颗星的平均评分拉低了！哦对了我是男的", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147051}, {"id": 4534, "content": "都是男司机", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 117714}, {"id": 4536, "content": " 一般都是我聊他", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 63439}, {"id": 4596, "content": "帅哒哒很有爱", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147401}, {"id": 4491, "content": "他总是朋友的朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146167}, {"id": 4511, "content": "不差钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142257}, {"id": 4519, "content": "很gentleman，不听乱七八糟的五毛钱电音，不拿两个手机吵吵抢单，电话来了还给挂掉，整体感觉比出租车好多了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 105318}, {"id": 5817, "content": "有个年轻男司机痞痞的，还有个老大叔可棒了在车里放污点的Song 2嗨得我舍不得下", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114671}, {"id": 5827, "content": "没碰到女生", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 140045}, {"id": 5829, "content": "微信号 duang419", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 140045}, {"id": 5739, "content": "屁，遇到一个接了我的单居然还接了另一个，然后因为别人跟他回家顺路就把我丢到路口，因为超过五分钟所以扣了我8块钱，他就说他给我叫个车他付车费，结果在雨里等着那个还在网吧里的司机来接我！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118263}, {"id": 6146, "content": "我们学校以前风味食堂以前某窗口的老板！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149916}, {"id": 6953, "content": "“你买了啥呀 这么香！” ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 111492}, {"id": 4157, "content": "“我外甥很不错，介绍你们认识呗！”", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 7506, "content": "我上次接了个明星……我朋友上次借了个明星……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145072}, {"id": 5722, "content": "上车帮我把行李放后备，下车也会帮拿下来，而出租车好的有前一个行为，后一个行为就是自己想多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4453, "content": "兴高采烈地介绍他们是怎么组队刷单的", "image": null, "praise_count": 39, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1218}, {"id": 4454, "content": "播放自己演唱的歌曲", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1218}, {"id": 4455, "content": "跟着音乐一起唱起来了，画面太美不敢看。", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114367}, {"id": 4456, "content": "喝红?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 8}, {"id": 4457, "content": "查户口", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 115358}, {"id": 4458, "content": "推销自己在卖的东西", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1218}, {"id": 4459, "content": "推荐别的乘客向他推荐的电影", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 3660}, {"id": 4460, "content": "为什么我遇到的司机都不怎么说话，我才是话多的那个……", "image": null, "praise_count": 50, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 139738}, {"id": 4464, "content": "是学长！", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 134885}, {"id": 4471, "content": "有的炫酷狂拽，一说赶时间就让我你好安全带带我飞，有的车辆破烂，一看就是专职司机", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146713}, {"id": 4472, "content": "表示自己已经过了为工作操劳的日子", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1375}, {"id": 4473, "content": "执拗的认为自己的翼虎是EVO", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 49435}, {"id": 4474, "content": "吐槽被出租车司机围追堵截", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146728}, {"id": 4477, "content": "飞行员，就爱在左转车道直行", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113353}, {"id": 4478, "content": "完全依赖导航。。。为什么？", "image": null, "praise_count": 127, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 117877}, {"id": 28799, "content": "现在我的uber司机，我完全可以和他车震～", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 289588}, {"id": 4480, "content": "哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": null}, {"id": 4481, "content": "不管怎样 反正比出租车司机好", "image": null, "praise_count": 103, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 54530}, {"id": 4492, "content": "约了一炮", "image": null, "praise_count": 129, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 44512}, {"id": 4495, "content": "一路循环凤凰传奇", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146201}, {"id": 4496, "content": "我经常遇到迫于生计来开uber的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142094}, {"id": 4499, "content": "想当年。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 107785}, {"id": 4500, "content": "各种神聊，无障碍沟通～～～", "image": null, "praise_count": 32, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146865}, {"id": 4503, "content": "毛病都很多，很jiubi", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146900}, {"id": 4504, "content": "人挺好的，真心的", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146909}, {"id": 4508, "content": "座位后边有瓶水啊…….没事没事你随便拿……（但我真的不渴！）", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 144784}, {"id": 4521, "content": "十八般武艺样样精通，什么话题都要聊。乘客也练就一身好武功，见招拆招。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142518}, {"id": 6071, "content": "大概播放器里是高原巨星专辑，回个家的路上像去了趟西藏。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149622}, {"id": 4540, "content": "各种逗比", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 66079}]}